  * Added results.xml output from any test case; adds libXML dependency
  * API change for logging functions; old versions deprecated (compiler warns)
  * Global log level reorganizing; pretty output with -auto (not default yet)
  * Test variants now printed when -s given
  * Examples for parameter variation with proper logging included
  * RPM source package name changed

